query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('tex')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('beamer',
'bibliographies',
'captions',
'color',
'errors',
'footnotes',
'natbib',
'packages',
'pdftex',
'sectioning',
'spacing',
'vertical-alignment',
'xetex');
